title: Faeries, Angels, Indians And Aliens: My Interdimensional Family
description:
Faeries, Angels, Indians And Aliens: My Interdimensional Family Volume 1 
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1440460035
ISBN-13: 978-1440460036
Author-Rex Patrick Haire, Ph.D.
Published- CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform (November 17, 2008)
Pages-663

 This is a spiritual counselor's deeply personal account of assistance given by beings from another dimension to help a suicidal woman overcome the devastating effects of sexual, physical and psychological traumas, and how they also helped her to become an amazingly adept channel for their humorous and inspiring messages for the human race. Commissioned by an angelic messenger, it is full of verbatim hypnotic sessions, conversatiions with interdimensional beings and miraculous events which proved the messengers were real. It reveals the spitual growth and loving relationships that evolved as a result of these conversations and events for all the entities involved, including the humans, the faeries, the angels, the Indian spirits and the aliens
